title: New, Spacious 6 bed/3 bath home for rent 10/1
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'This two-story, beautiful, large home in a fabulous community could be yours!', 'This house boasts oversized rooms and vaulted ceilings throughout.', 'Seated on a private, grassy 3/4 acre lot, there is room to play!', 'There is a large master bedroom with a full bathroom, soaking tub and a walk-in closet.', 'There are 4 other bedrooms; 3 on the upper level, one on the main level and two in the basement.', 'Laundry is on the upper level right outside of the master suite-', 'so convenient!', 'The main level is entirely open concept for the whole family to enjoy time together.', 'Convenient location near beaches, highway access, shopping and historic downtown White Bear Lake.', 'Schedule a showing today, this rental will go fast!', 'Available October 1', 'Application Fee: $50/adult', 'Rent: $3450', 'Security Deposit $3450', '1-3 year lease options available', 'Dogs and cats okay, pet rent extra', 'No smoking', 'Qualifications: Income must be 2x rent, must pass income, criminal, rental history and credit background checks.', 'full video walk through of 2477 County Road F: <URL>']
